data.title: Guttigomphus avilionis gen. et sp. nov., a trirachodontid cynodont from the upper Cynognathus Assemblage Zone, Burgersdorp Formation of South Africa
data.meta_description: The Burgersdorp Formation of South Africa is a richly fossiliferous rock sequence at the top of the Permian-Triassic Beaufort Group and is known for its abundance of Early-Middle Triassic vertebrate remains, particularly cynodonts.
